## Data Attribution

The dataset used in this project (`data/paper/`) is sourced from:

> Goh, G., Vesterdorf, K., Fuller, A., Blache, D., & Maloney, S. K. (2024).
> *Optimal sampling interval for characterisation of the circadian rhythm of body
> temperature in homeothermic animals.*
> Ecology and Evolution, 14(4), e11243.
> https://doi.org/10.1002/ece3.11243
>
> Data available via Dryad: https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.1g1jwsv46

The dataset is published under the Dryad default license (CC0 1.0 / CC-BY).
Please cite the original paper if you use the data in your own work.
